                            <comment id="12994442" author="rding" created="Mon, 14 Feb 2011 19:36:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-4012&quot; title=&quot;Providing splitting support for bzip2 compressed files&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HADOOP-4012&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HADOOP-4012&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; added support for concatenated bzip2 files, but the fix is only available for version 21 or higher. In the future, Pig may consider to drop its own bzip2 support and use Hadoop&apos;s bzip2 code directly.  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
